#. type: Title ==
#: ../src/redstone-link.adoc:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "Operating Principle"
msgstr "工作原理"

#. type: #principle
#: ../src/redstone-link.adoc:25
msgid "A redstone link has 2 modes of operation:"
msgstr "无线红石信号终端有两种模式："

#. type: horizontal
#: ../src/redstone-link.adoc:28
msgid ""
"Sends the powered state of its incoming redstone connections to other "
"redstone links on the same channel."
msgstr "把输入红石连接的充能状态发送给同频道的其他无线红石信号终端。"

#. type: horizontal
#: ../src/redstone-link.adoc:29
msgid ""
"Receives from other redstone links on the same channel. If any of them is "
"powered, it powers its outgoing redstone connections."
msgstr ""
"接收同频道其他终端的状态。只要其中任意一个处于充能状态，就会使自身的输出红石"
"连接充能。"

#. type: horizontal
#: ../src/redstone-link.adoc:31
msgid ""
"Redstone links are distinguished by channels, which consists of 2 item "
"types. Each channel carries a redstone signal independently of the others. "
"Examples of distinct channels are:"
msgstr "每个频道由两种物品共同确定，不同组合彼此独立。例如以下频道均不相同："

#. type: horizontal
#: ../src/redstone-link.adoc:33
msgid "(Oak Plank, Cobblestone)"
msgstr "（橡木木板，圆石）"

#. type: horizontal
#: ../src/redstone-link.adoc:34
msgid "(Oak Plank, Air)"
msgstr "（橡木木板，空气）"

#. type: horizontal
#: ../src/redstone-link.adoc:35
msgid "(Air, Oak Plank)"
msgstr "（空气，橡木木板）"

#. type: horizontal
#: ../src/redstone-link.adoc:36
msgid "(Air, Air)"
msgstr "（空气，空气）"

#. type: #configuration
#: ../src/redstone-link.adoc:41
msgid ""
"After placing a redstone link on the virtual board, clicking the component "
"opens its configuration screen."
msgstr "将无线红石信号终端放到虚拟面板后，点击组件以打开设置界面。"

#. type: Block title
#: ../src/redstone-link.adoc:42
#, no-wrap
msgid "Redstone link settings"
msgstr "无线红石信号终端设置界面"

#. type: #configuration
#: ../src/redstone-link.adoc:47
msgid ""
"❶ ❷ Channel:: Place an item, or drag a ghost item from JEI, to set the "
"channel of the redstone link."
msgstr "❶ ❷ 频道:: 放入物品，或从 JEI 拖入虚拟物品，以设置终端频道。"

#. type: #configuration
#: ../src/redstone-link.adoc:50
msgid ""
"❸ Relocate button:: Click to move the location of this redstone link on the "
"virtual board."
msgstr "❸ 移动组件按钮:: 在虚拟面板上移动此终端。"

#. type: #configuration
#: ../src/redstone-link.adoc:53
msgid ""
"❹ Add connection button:: Click to connect to other components via redstone. "
"Directions of connections are decided automatically. Send-mode links may "
"only have incoming connections, receive-mode links may only have outgoing "
"connections."
msgstr ""
"❹ 新建连接按钮:: 通过红石连接到其他组件。连接方向会自动确定，发送模式只能接收"
"输入连接，接收模式只能建立输出连接。"

#. type: #configuration
#: ../src/redstone-link.adoc:56
msgid ""
"❺ Mode switch:: Click to switch between send image:btn-send-mode.png[,18,18] "
"and receive image:btn-receive-mode.png[,18,18] modes."
msgstr ""
"❺ 模式切换:: 在发送 image:btn-send-mode.png[,18,18] 和接收 image:btn-receive-"
"mode.png[,18,18] 模式之间切换。"

#. type: #configuration
#: ../src/redstone-link.adoc:58
msgid "❻ Confirm button:: Click to confirm settings and close the screen."
msgstr "❻ 确认按钮:: 保存设置并关闭界面。"
